Redondo_Beach.Del Aire, California:
Del Aire is a census-designated place (CDP) in Los Angeles County, California, United States. The population was 10,001 at the 2010 census, up from 9,012 at the 2000 census.
Del Aire is a tiny unincorporated middle-class residential neighborhood next to the giant interchange where Interstate 405 and Interstate 105 meet.
